REACT Setup Webpack for dev environment


PACKAGE JSON
npm init -y  
npm install --save react react-dom
npm install --save-dev webpack
npm install --save-dev babel-core babel-loader          - transforms jsx into js for browsers
npm install --save-dev babel-preset-react babel-preset-es2015

.babelrc in root
{
  "presets": ["react", "es2015"]
}

CONFIGURING WEBPACK - installed locally above 
Local run webpack in terminal with: node_modules/.bin/webpack
globally run webpack with: webpack           - npm install --save-dev webpack

package.json
"build": "webpack"   add to scripts
    Then you can run build as - npm run build


webpack.config.js - in the root
      module.exports =  {
        entry: './app.js',

        output: {
         path: 'build',
        filename: 'bundle.js'
        },

        module: {
         loaders: [
            {
              test: /\.js$/,
             exclude: /node_modules/,
             loader: 'babel-loader'
           }
          ]
        }
      };

app.js
      import React from 'react';
      import ReactDOM from 'react-dom';
      
index.html
      <script src="bundle.js"></script>
